2021. 
The goal is to place sensors and actuators on the raspberry or take advantage of the already built in in order to gather and collect data, set a case scanario scene for example, 
for security purposes whilst communicating with a smart phone application and send notifications.
The sensors placed on raspberry are placed through the pins in the pins accordingly based on the documentation. There's usually a ground a input power pin and the rest of the pins
usually are in order to communicate the raspberry with the sensor as well as the data transferring. 
